name: Pehuén - Tree of Life II
description:
2/8

Way south, where the days are long and the land is wide, 
the Araucaria will remain evergreen over the years to come.
It is said you can luckily find a mighty specimen of its kind,
with its massive trunk in a hidden valley lost in the heights. 
Even God was fed on its fruit, from the ground as a gift. 
The past and wisdom live in its leaves.
